OL,3,CShoplifting in Devon and Cornwall sees
OL,4,Cincrease double the national average
OL,6,FShoplifting is on the rise in Devon
OL,7,Fand Cornwall, at a much quicker rate
OL,8,Fthan the rest of the country.
OL,10,FThe Office of National Statistics has
OL,11,Frevealed shoplifting has increased by
OL,12,F46% in a year (between September 2023
OL,13,F- September 2024) in Devon and
OL,14,FCornwall.
OL,16,FNationally, there was a 23% increase
OL,17,Fin that time period.
OL,19,FOn Tuesday 25 March shoplifters were
OL,20,Ftargeted in an undercover police
OL,21,Foperation in Exeter.
