OL,3,CShoplifting in Devon and Cornwall sees
OL,4,Cincrease double the national average
OL,6,FOfficers carried out searches to
OL,7,Ftackle repeat offenders.
OL,9,FThis included working with Exeter
OL,10,FBusinesses Against Crime (EBAC) and
OL,11,Fthe local council CCTV.
OL,13,FBy the end of the day, six people were
OL,14,Fsearched. From this, two were found to
OL,15,Fhave stolen goods which were returned
OL,16,Fto the stores. As they were under 18,
OL,17,Fthe individuals were referred to a
OL,18,Fyouth justice team to prevent
OL,19,Freoffending.
