OL,3,CShoplifting in Devon and Cornwall sees
OL,4,Cincrease double the national average
OL,6,FThere were also three safeguarding
OL,7,Freferrals, and an illegal e-bike was
OL,8,Fseized.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for the force said: "We
OL,11,Fare aware this is a prominent issue in
OL,12,Four communities, so our Neighbourhood
OL,13,FTeams and officers are out in hotspot
OL,14,Fareas conducting high visibility
OL,15,Fpatrols, building relationships and
OL,16,Fengaging with business communities,
OL,17,Fworking with partners to give crime
OL,18,Fprevention advice to stores and
OL,19,Fidentifying prolific offenders in an
OL,20,Feffort to build public confidence and
OL,21,Fdeter shoplifting.
