OL,3,CShoplifting in Devon and Cornwall sees
OL,4,Cincrease double the national average
OL,6,FWhen asked if it's an 'endless game of
OL,7,Fcat and mouse', Sergeant Andy Walton,
OL,8,Ffrom Devon and Cornwall Police, said:
OL,9,F"To some degree, you could say that.
OL,10,FBut we are working with courts, we are
OL,11,Fworking with probation services as
OL,12,Fwell and we try to look at what orders
OL,13,Fwe can put in place to curtail that
OL,14,Fneed people feel to shoplift."
