OL,6,FInspector Nathan Johnson: "We know
OL,7,Fwhat shoplifting often comes from
OL,8,Faddiction but most of our successes
OL,9,Faround shoplifting are away from the
OL,10,Fcity centre and it's about our
OL,11,Fintelligence department that let us
OL,12,Fknow what our top six offenders are
OL,13,Ffor the month and then we will go and
OL,14,Farrest them.
OL,16,F"In the last month those six are
OL,17,Feither in prison or on bail waiting a
OL,18,Fprison sentence.
